<h2>Oath Discovered</h2>
<h3>— Cosita —</h3>

<p>
If this were Deepwoken, this would be the moment where the screen fades in,
the wind starts to sound, and you realize you’re about to begin something
that will change you forever.
</p>

<p>
I want you to know something before anything else:  
I love listening to you talk about the things you love.  
When you explain something with excitement, when your voice changes because
you’re passionate, I swear my heart slows down just to hear you better.
</p>

<p>
I love playing Deepwoken with you, even when we fail, even when things go wrong,
even when we have to start over.  
I love Valorant with you too — not because of the game, but because it’s us,
learning, laughing, messing up, improving together.
</p>

<p>
I love doing new things with you.  
Cutting your hair, drawing together, listening to music side by side, laughing
until we can’t breathe because of tickles.  
I love walking with you, exploring, imagining our future while our feet move
forward.
</p>

<p>
I want to know Iceland with you.  
I want cold air, quiet streets, shared meals, silly moments, and long talks.
I love watching The Boondocks with you, eating together, sharing time —
because time with you feels real.
</p>

<p>
I love everything about you.  
And every single time I see you smile, my eyes literally shine.
It makes me want to see that smile for the rest of my life.
</p>

<p>
Maybe I’m not the perfect person for you.  
Maybe I’m not “the one” by the rules of the world.  
But I know this: I don’t want to know anyone else.
</p>

